Hana Hatae https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hana_Hatae 0 Hana Rebecca Hatae (born July 15, 1988) is an American actress. As a child actress, her first role was as Molly O'Brien in Star Trek: The Next Generation and Star Trek: Deep Space Nine, a role which she reprised in the fan-made series Star Trek: Renegades.
